Package: airies-ups
Version: @VERSION@
Section: net
Priority: optional
Architecture: @ARCH@
Maintainer: XxI0NICxX <vifair22@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://git.airies.net/vifair22/airies-ups-c
Depends: libc6, libmodbus5, libsqlite3-0, libcurl4t64 | libcurl4, libmicrohttpd12t64 | libmicrohttpd12, libssl3t64 | libssl3, systemd, adduser
Recommends: udev
Description: APC and CyberPower UPS management daemon
 airies-ups is a self-contained UPS management daemon that talks
 directly to UPS hardware over Modbus RTU (APC SMT/SRT) or USB HID
 (APC Back-UPS, CyberPower PowerPanel). Replaces APC PowerChute and
 NUT for these device families.
 .
 Includes a web UI served by the daemon (no separate web server
 needed), Pushover alerting, weather-aware HE mode toggling, and
 orchestrated shutdown of dependent hosts.
